data.description: **Gladly accepting back-up offers.**Experience the pride of ownership and joyful living in this 4 bed 2 1/2 bath home.  On the pond, fully fenced, and complete with a private screen-covered and heated pool, this home makes the long Florida summers a blast.  The private master suite is downstairs, his and hers closest with remaining beds/baths on the second floor in addition to a loft/flex room.  Further specifications include; New carpet 2019 along with brand new just added in the den last month. Pool built 2020. Water softener added, new fridge & dishwasher 2021. Exterior of house painted 2023. Newly cleaned and sealed pavers. Irrigation well in place. Laundry room upgraded with ample storage. Expansive pantry. Double ovens. Microwave. Cook top. Safe Touch security along with Arlo security cameras throughout and Arlo doorbell.
